{"lemma":"مُؤَنَّثٌ","slug":"مُؤَنَّثٌ","root":"#.ن.ث","root_slug":"_-ن-ث","root_link":"/words/roots/_-ن-ث","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["adj","noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":false}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"feminine","tags":["feminine"]},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"feminine","tags":["feminine","general"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"feminine","tags":["feminine"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Derived from the passive participle of the verb أَنَّثَ (ʔannaṯa, “to make feminine”)."},"ipa":["/mu.ʔan.naθ/"],"lanes_definition":null,"classical_definitions":{"source":"hawramani","url":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/%D9%85%D8%A4%D9%86%D8%AB/","headword_ar":"مؤنث","entries":[{"lexicon_id":"dictionary_18","lexicon_en":"Al-Sharīf al-Jurjānī, Kitāb al-Taʿrīfāt (d. 1413 CE)","lexicon_ar":"كتاب التعريفات للشريف الجرجاني","permalink":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=23784#5283a3","body_html":"<span>المؤنث اللفظي: ما فيه علامة التأنيث لفظًا، نحو ضاربة، وحبلى، وحمراء، أو تقديرًا، وهو التاء، نحو: أرض، تردها في التصغير، نحو: أريضة.<br></span><br>المؤنث الحقيقي: ما بإزائه ذَكر من الحيوان، كامرأة وناقة، وغير الحقيقي ما لم يكن كذلك بل يتعلق بالوضع والاصطلاح، كالظلمة، والأرض، وغيرهما."}]}}